The roof top area of the hotel is wonderful and views good over the city and a great place to relax after a busy day sightseeing.	The terrace & pool on the roof was beautifull, a relaxing place to sit in the sun with nice cocktails.	The best bit is the roof terrace, with pool to cool down in after a long day sight seeing.	The pool area was clean everyday and there is bar service and food available at poolside if required.